 Here are the changes I would make to add a separate staff UI for each rank showing online status and weekly playtime:

1. Create a enum for the different staff ranks:

```java
enum StaffRank {
  MOD,
  ADMIN,
  OWNER
}
```

2. Create a separate inventory for each rank:

```java 
private Inventory modGUI;
private Inventory adminGUI;
private Inventory ownerGUI;

// Initialize in onEnable
modGUI = Bukkit.createInventory(null, 27, ChatColor.DARK_GREEN + "Mod Staff");
adminGUI = Bukkit.createInventory(null, 27, ChatColor.DARK_GREEN + "Admin Staff"); 
ownerGUI = Bukkit.createInventory(null, 27, ChatColor.DARK_GREEN + "Owner Staff");
```

3. When getting the online staff, also store their rank:

```java
