 Hier is een voorbeeld hoe je het in een aparte class kan implementeren:

```java
public class StaffPlaytimeManager {

  // Required weekly playtime per rank
  private Map<String, Integer> requiredPlaytime = new HashMap<>();

  // Tracker for weekly playtime
  private PlaytimeTracker playtimeTracker;

  public StaffPlaytimeManager() {
    requiredPlaytime.put("staff.mod", 10); 
    requiredPlaytime.put("staff.admin", 15);
    requiredPlaytime.put("staff.owner", 20);

    playtimeTracker = new PlaytimeTracker();
  }

  // Run every week
  public void checkRequiredPlaytime() {

    // Loop through online players
    for(Player player : Bukkit.getOnlinePlayers()) {

      // Get rank and required playtime
      String rank = getRank(player);
      int required = requiredPlaytime.get(rank);

      // Get weekly playtime
      int weeklyPlaytime = playtimeTracker.getWeeklyPlaytime(player);

      // Check if met required
      if(weeklyPlaytime < required) {
        punish(player); 
      } else {
        reward(player);
      }

    }

    // Reset tracker
    playtimeTracker.resetWeeklyPlaytime();

  }

  public void punish(Player player) {
    // punishment code
  }

  public void reward(Player player) {
    // reward code
  }

}
```

Je kan deze class aanroepen vanuit je main plugin class om elke week de check uit te voeren.

